1
00:00:18,125 --> 00:00:20,875
LJUBAV, SMRT I ROBOTI

2
00:00:28,875 --> 00:00:33,250
BLISKI SUSRETI MALE VRSTE

3
00:00:43,416 --> 00:00:45,500
To, stiglo je pojačanje!

4
00:00:46,625 --> 00:00:48,833
Samo polako. Sve ćemo riješiti.

5
00:00:49,333 --> 00:00:51,791
Pratite mene, dečki. Do večere smo doma.

6
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:56,915
Dobro, idem.

7
00:00:56,916 --> 00:00:57,958
Stani malo!

8
00:00:58,833 --> 00:01:01,582
Ljudi, dolazimo u miru.

9
00:01:01,583 --> 00:01:06,624
Dugo smo putovali, ali sretni smo
što smo ovdje zajedno s vama.

10
00:01:06,625 --> 00:01:07,625
Naoružan je!

11
00:01:12,375 --> 00:01:13,208
Čovječe!

12
00:01:14,291 --> 00:01:15,791
- Još je živ!
- Drž' ga!

13
00:01:18,666 --> 00:01:19,875
Pa jeboga pas!

14
00:01:22,791 --> 00:01:24,041
Ovamo dođi! Majku mu!

15
00:01:25,791 --> 00:01:27,458
U vražju mater, još je živ!

16
00:01:51,458 --> 00:01:53,958
Bože mili! Nikad kraja!

17
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:56,666
Lijepa moja cura!

18
00:01:58,750 --> 00:02:00,333
Da srknem malo.

19
00:02:02,458 --> 00:02:05,749
Ništa se ti ne obaziri, sad ću ja...

20
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:07,750
Bože mili! O, ne!

21
00:02:12,333 --> 00:02:14,625
Pustite me van!

22
00:02:15,375 --> 00:02:18,791
Koji je ovo vrag? Ne!

23
00:02:22,958 --> 00:02:24,957
Stigli su!

24
00:02:24,958 --> 00:02:27,000
Sve će nas naguziti!

25
00:02:31,708 --> 00:02:34,666
Ne, čekajte! Uzmite mene!

26
00:02:55,541 --> 00:02:59,041
SAMO MIRNO DALJE

27
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:08,290
VETERANI INOZEMNIH RATOVA

28
00:03:08,291 --> 00:03:09,750
Podigni i gurni mu.

29
00:03:10,416 --> 00:03:11,540
U usta!

30
00:03:11,541 --> 00:03:12,833
Naprijed!

31
00:03:13,333 --> 00:03:15,999
To! Eto vam ga na! Hura!

32
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,999
PIVNICA GREYFRIARS

33
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,625
Natrag na Mjesec! Marš!

34
00:03:22,833 --> 00:03:24,666
Marš na Mjesec!

35
00:03:26,458 --> 00:03:28,458
Raspali, brate! Gore su!

36
00:03:32,708 --> 00:03:37,375
SJEDINJENE ZEMALJSKE DRŽAVE

37
00:03:59,458 --> 00:04:00,291
Vozi!

38
00:04:09,875 --> 00:04:12,250
Ne još! Vozi!

39
00:04:32,416 --> 00:04:33,333
Ne!

40
00:04:36,833 --> 00:04:37,665
Može!

41
00:04:37,666 --> 00:04:39,582
LJUDI SU ZAKON

42
00:04:39,583 --> 00:04:41,333
Gotovi ste, mamicu vam vašu!

43
00:04:41,833 --> 00:04:48,833
{\an8}NABIJEMO VAS NA SONDU
OVO NIJE VAŠ PLANET

44
00:06:09,791 --> 00:06:11,875
Prijevod titlova: Sandra Mlađenović

